headline: Illinois Kicks off 2026 With Support That Shows up for Substance Use Disorder
summary: CHICAGO, January 06, 2026--Wayspring, an organization dedicated to advancing care for substance use disorder (SUD), and Aetna Better Health® of Illinois, a CVS Health® company, have teamed up to deliver a new model of recovery care for Illinois Medicaid members — one that shows up, breaks down barriers and makes lasting recovery possible.

headline: CVS Health declares quarterly dividend
summary: CVS Health® (NYSE: CVS) has announced that its board of directors has approved a quarterly dividend of sixty-six and one-half cents ($0.665 cents) per share on the Common Stock of the Corporation. The dividend is payable on February 2, 2026, to holders of record on January 22, 2026.
